### Domain 5 — ChapterPage

> [!WARNING]
> **Schema fix required**: The current `ChapterPage` entity has a `ManuscriptId` FK that should not exist. `ChapterPage` represents the final published page of a **Chapter** — it has no business relationship with a `Manuscript` (which is the draft submission). The fix involves: removing `ManuscriptId` + `Manuscript` nav-prop from the entity, removing the FK configuration from `MangaDbContext`, and creating a new EF Core migration.

