7. PageTask + PageTaskSubmission (depends on Chapter, Manuscript)
8. Annotation (depends on Manuscript)
9. BoardDecision + BoardVote (depends on Series)
10. VoteRecord + RankingSnapshot (depends on Series)
11. Notification + UserNotification (depends on User)
12. UserAssignment (depends on User)
13. Escalation (depends on Series, User)
14. Wire up all DI registrations + AutoMapper profiles
15. Build & verify Swagger

